{"tid":2022849,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"立法會平機會主席大戰葉劉淑儀","createTime":"2020-05-18T14:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T15:08:43.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c57f9c61f489fa3ef4cd297351dfe39a88f8da09","tid":2022849,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:39:14.000Z","msg":"立法會政制事務委員會今午（18日）召開會議，新民黨主席葉劉淑儀會上罕見與平機會主席朱敏健互轟。朱敏健提到武漢肺炎疫情發生後，部份內地來港人士遇到不合理對待，有餐廳甚至貼上告示，表明拒絕招待內地人士，但現行法例未賦予平機會足夠權力處理，令會方只可發表強硬措辭的聲明，無法執法，希望未來可修改法例應對。<span style=\"color: red;\">葉劉則批評朱敏健「大隻講」，指其聽取坊間意見後，應向政制及內地事務局提交修改立法建議，斥他很多事情只講不做，應該要被「炒魷魚」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n朱敏健不滿葉劉有關批評，指平機會「又講又做」，<span style=\"color: red;\">聲稱若用葉劉建議的態度處事，「咁根本唔使搵我啦，呢個係一個郵政信箱嘅態度，有人同你講一樣嘢，你就擰轉頭同政府講不如去做。」說法令葉劉激動大怒，高聲力斥：「喂，朱總裁！你咁講嘢荒謬喎！」批評朱的回應「有無搞錯？」又問朱「有無讀過書㗎？」</span>............<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200518/P2SZSHYV6NCAH4J6SIV5S54MFY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200518%2FP2SZSHYV6NCAH4J6SIV5S54MFY%2F&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkChx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=4caa2ce2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200518%2FP2SZSHYV6NCAH4J6SIV5S54MFY%2F&h=ab99644d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200518/P2SZSHYV6NCAH4J6SIV5S54MFY/</a><br />\n蘋果有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180fc01a4e52fe16489baad91f8d251abdf505fe","tid":2022849,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e648d86e28959dc5bc754a2b3e1bc970a132bd","tid":2022849,"uid":261913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:44:10.000Z","msg":"姐姐今次仲唔滅黨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bcbbe6ed023cc4e9db680eb516d7d56c62317be","tid":2022849,"uid":40337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c